<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmatu śubhaśakavarṣaṁbbulu 
<lb n="2"/>142<unclear>7</unclear> Agunēṁṭi raktākṣi saṁvva 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>tsara māgha śu 11 gu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> nāṁḍu ci 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>durele Ayaṁgāru tama taṁ 
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ḍri Allāḍayyaṁgārikinnita 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ma talli Ānaṁtammakunu pu 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṇyaṁgānu nilipi pratiṣṭha ceśi 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>na hanumaṁttuṁḍu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrī 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>hanumaṁttayyaku 
<lb n="10"/>Amutupaḷaku vū 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ri dakṣaṇapū dikku daṁḍamu 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ni cēnu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrī 
</p>

